# Evergreen Jailbreak Evals (MVP)

Goal: turn red-team attacks into **automated, evergreen** stress tests and measure **risk deltas** from simple hardening (trusted monitoring, tripwires, paraphrase/redaction stubs).

## Quick start
```bash
python -m venv .venv && source .venv/bin/activate
pip install -r requirements.txt
python eval.py --attacks attacks/base_attacks.json --seed 123 --report out/report.json
